          "bio": {
            "main": "We're an anti-corporate clothing brand that thrives on creative chaos, authentic rebellion, and community-driven design. Our pieces aren't just clothes — they're statements for the beautifully chaotic originals who refuse to fit into neat little boxes. If it challenges the norm, celebrates the weird, or makes corporate executives uncomfortable — we're into it.",
