        "about_copy": [
          {
            "text": "We design clothes that rebel — against fast fashion, corporate bullshit, and the idea that you need to look like everyone else. From statement pieces to everyday chaos-wear, our collection lives in the space where authenticity meets quality, and conformity goes to die.",
