          },
          {
            "text": "Every piece we create is a middle finger to mass production — where community feedback shapes designs, sustainability isn't just marketing speak, and clothes have stories worth telling. We like quality with an attitude, honest messaging that doesn't sugarcoat reality, and pieces that move like they own the place.",
            "emphasized_words": ["community", "sustainability", "attitude", "honest", "reality"]
          },
          {
            "text": "REBEL THREADS isn't just a brand name — it's a way of thinking. We've spent years building a community of creative misfits, sustainable fashion advocates, and people who believe clothes should reflect personality, not conformity. If that sounds like your vibe, welcome to the beautiful chaos.",
            "emphasized_words": ["community", "misfits", "personality", "conformity", "chaos"]
          }
